 In the manuscript a sketch of a pointing hand and two asterisks appear at the beginning of the first paragraph of this document. See also <a href="default.xqy?keys=GEWN-print-03-03-02-0269&amp;expandNote=GEWN-03-03-02-0269-fn-0001#GEWN-03-03-02-0269-fn-0001" class="document">General Orders, 26 Feb. 1776, n.1</a>.</p>

